2021.11.21造訪星期天大概17:00點初頭去，不用排隊可直接有位置。吃完18:00多外面已經大排長龍了⋯⋯小碗牛肉麵$170（聽說之後會漲價）有4片牛肉，牛肉相較一般牛肉麵店的牛肉來說真的很軟嫩，麵和湯頭就比較普通。調味區有帶有一點香料味的辣油，一定要嘗嘗看！另外，若想吃牛筋，建議直接點半筋半肉牛肉麵（小碗牛肉、牛筋各3），裡面的牛筋比單點一盤牛筋來得軟（單點$160、量不多而且很硬）If you’re not up for lining up on weekend nights, come at around 17:00 and you shall not wait in line. The queue will be long around 18:00. The small beef noodles had 4 pieces of beef, which were pretty soft compared to the other shops out there! The broth and noodles were just average. I recommend people try the spicy butter - I guess they added some spices inside to create the special taste. The beef tendons in the half tendon half beef noodles were way softer than the ones of the beef tendon plate. If you’re looking for softer tendons, then I suggest to just order the half tendon half beef noodles.
